ina]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 3 || 3:00\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2014-08-31 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|ITA}} Elisa Qualizza || [[2014 in Kunlun Fight#Kunlun Fight 9|Kunlun Fight 9 - 2014 Legend of Mulan Tournament, Quarter Finals]] || [[Shangqiu|Shangqiu, China]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 3 || 3:00\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2013-06-22 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|PAR}} Fabiana Dutra|| Defensa & Combatante || [[Paraguay]] || TKO (Spinning back kick to the body) || 1 || N/A\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2013-03-02 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|MEX}} Malena Mu\u00f1oz|| WKC K-1 World Championships 2013 || [[Lima, Peru]] || TKO (Spinning back kick to the body) || 1 || 2:30\n|- \n! style=background:white colspan=9 |Retains the WKC K-1 Lightweight World Championship -60&nbsp;kg\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2013-01-06 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|MEX}} Tania Gonzales|| WKC K-1 World Championships 2013 || [[Mexico]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 3 || 3:00\n|- \n! style=background:white colspan=9 |Wins the WKC K-1 Lightweight World Championship -60&nbsp;kg\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2012-12-02 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|BRA}} Patricia Silva|| N/A || [[Porto Alegre, Brazil]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 4 || 3:00\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2012-08-24 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|ARG}} Laura Soledad Griffa|| K-1 event in Peru || [[Lima, Peru]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 4 || 3:00\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2012-04-28 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|FRA}} Ielo Page || Double championnat du monde WMC || [[Brest, France]] || Decision (Unanimous) || 5 || 3:00\n|- \n! style=background:white colspan=9 |Wins the [[World Muaythai Council#Female world champions|WMC Muaythai Female Super Lightweight World Champion]].\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2011-11-06 || Win ||